summary: A project focusing on making Skyrim a more delicious place.
descriptionHtml:
PROJECT DELICIOUS SKYRIM
---------------------------------------

This is a test-release of the first texture in what is planned to become a big, tasty overhaul.
The focus of this mod is making the food in skyrim more delicious and good looking.

Later, when the tools are released, the plan is to also release lots of completely new food.

0.1 RELEASE:
- Delicious Bread [custom HQ texture and normal for the bread]

UPDATE:
- Added the Eidar Cheese as an optional update.
Fun facts: After some hardcore searching I actually managed to find the exact same cheese texture used by Bethesda.
You can see it pretty clearly in the comparison pictures.
author: KimonJ
